  "body": "Every time we import a block and we receive a VALID from the EL in `onExecutionPayloadResult`, we always try to remove FinalizedOptimisticTransitionPayload from the Storage\r\n\r\nso in `MergeTransitionBlockValidator#verifyFinalizedTransitionBlock` we call:\r\n\r\n<img width=\"666\" alt=\"image\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/15999009/191313133-ecbd66c5-e4d5-4e29-87a7-82faaadfd1d3.png\">\r\n\r\nthis will set `clearFinalizedOptimisticTransitionPayload` to `true` in transaction.\r\n\r\nthis will then cause `optimisticTransitionBlockRootSet` to be `true` when creating `StorageUpdate`: \r\n<img width=\"488\" alt=\"image\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/15999009/191313945-b5562eb4-fb4d-4a86-9d49-dca9cfc73812.png\">\r\n\r\nend we end up being always synchronous due to:\r\n\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/15999009/191314490-32ff1d31-c3ba-4c8f-ad18-e0ce1d633f57.png)",
